[[div class="toc-right"]]
[[div style="writing-mode: vertical-rl; font-family: 'UnGungseo'; font-size:1.6em; margin: auto; float:right;"]]
[[span class="ruby"]]銀[[span class="rt"]]은[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]山[[span class="rt"]]산[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]漠[[span class="rt"]]막[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]漠[[span class="rt"]]막[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]難[[span class="rt"]]난[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]尋[[span class="rt"]]심[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]岸[[span class="rt"]]안[[/span]][[/span]]
[[span class="ruby"]]玉[[span class="rt"]]옥[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]海[[span class="rt"]]해[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]茫[[span class="rt"]]망[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]茫[[span class="rt"]]망[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]未[[span class="rt"]]미[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]見[[span class="rt"]]견[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]津[[span class="rt"]]진[[/span]][[/span]]
[[span class="ruby"]]萬[[span class="rt"]]만[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]逕[[span class="rt"]]경[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]人[[span class="rt"]]인[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]稀[[span class="rt"]]희[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]飛[[span class="rt"]]비[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]鳥[[span class="rt"]]조[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]絶[[span class="rt"]]절[[/span]][[/span]]
[[span class="ruby"]]乾[[span class="rt"]]건[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]坤[[span class="rt"]]곤[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]到[[span class="rt"]]도[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]此[[span class="rt"]]차[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]便[[span class="rt"]]변[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]淸[[span class="rt"]]청[[/span]][[/span]][[span class="ruby"]]新[[span class="rt"]]신[[/span]][[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="float:right;"]]
은빛 산 막막하여 [[span class="ruby"]]언덕[[span class="rt"]]오만함[[/span]][[/span]]을 찾기 어렵고
옥 같은 물 망망하여 [[span class="ruby"]]나루[[span class="rt"]]찐득함[[/span]][[/span]]가 보이지 않네
만 갈래 길에 사람은 적고 새들도 날지 않아
